# commands
# p: Pause display
# T: Display Accummulative Total
# D: Dest port Display
# S: Source Port Display
# t: Toggle display of the traffic summary.
# n: Toggle the display of hostnames and IP addresses.
# b: Display Traffic Bars per connection
# h: Display options
# q: Quit iftop.


